I am new to this board, and only started posting recently when members of my guild who are veterans here thought it would be a good idea.  I like seeing who is going to Hate or Air, not because I believe they have some kind of lock on the camp, but so I know what to expect when I get there if we were to host a raid.  Chances are I will not go at same time cause its better ROI for my guild if we dont.<br>
